e,"pull":true}},"body":"In the same way that `authorize` accepts a symbol, it would be nice if `permitted_attributes` also accepted a symbol.\n\nBecause `permitted_attributes` only accepts an object you end up with some ugly chicken and egg code in `create` actions:\n\n``` ruby\ndef create\n    authorize(:post)\n   # Need a post before I can use permitted_attributes\n   @post = Post.new\n   @post.update_attributes permitted_attributes(@post)\n   ...\nend\n```\n\nThis would be nicer:\n\n``` ruby\ndef create\n   authorize(:post)\n   @post = Post.new permitted_attributes(:post)\n   ...\nend\n```\n\nI would be happy to contribute a PR if that is something you would accept.\n","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/varvet/pundit/issues/299/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/varvet/pundit/issues/299/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"completed"}},"event":"cross-referenced"},{"id":514977347,"node_id":"MDExOkNsb3NlZEV2ZW50NTE0OTc3MzQ3","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/varvet/pundit/issues/events/514977347","actor":null,"event":"closed","commit_id":"9862b6024985d67214dd5dd93c3b347e5b2b718c","commit_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/varvet/pundit/commits/9862b6024985d67214dd5dd93c3b347e5b2b718c","created_at":"2016-01-14T13:43:58Z","state_reason":null,"performed_via_github_app":null},{"actor":{"login":"md5","id":76367,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjc2MzY3","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/76367?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/md5","html_url":"https://github.com/md5","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/md5/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/md5/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/md5/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/md5/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/md5/subscr